tent.com/a-/ACB-R5RXpz1MGyQ2MtnGQYgOiECbDuzz_w6oDqcK4up_uA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 meses","text":"Son profesionales y confianza en el trato.\nMejor precio del mercado en Sevilla.\nSara, la dependienta q me atendió fue encantadora.\nSi lo necesito , volveré a contar con su servicio","time":1677322443,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Inma Bizcocho Bañez","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109535211020603565848/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACB-R5StQl1DidfDjInZC3fDdQiU49guJauzPtN_u0CZ3qY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 1 mes","text":"100% recomendable, muy amable Sara, que me atendió. Muy simpática y atenta durante el servicio prestado.","time":1680688745,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Agostina Verdini","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113592692193936931795/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxYO0ScNMc_mXjXx6PqM_g8pdwZ1soN92gUtF0ol=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace una semana","text":"Muy buen servicio y trato. Ángela ha tenido muchísima paciencia y me ha atendido genial.gracias","time":1683636801,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Jose Manuel Carvajal Nuñez","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118244590684249436379/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxbs80kCNRqIT4yf2_0gDYJqZWfi2ZNS-8gJxuw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 semanas","text":"Muy profesional.\nLa señorita Belen nos atendió con mucha simpatía y profesionalidad.\nMuy buen precio.","time":1683051940,"translated":false}],"types":["jewelry_store","finance","store","point_of_interest","establishment"],"url":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=3222053015547448597","user_rat